        public java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Long> parse()

        parse the string and return a map to determine send packet delay. The last is default value for other processes

        Format: a(id)=b(delay),c(id)=d(delay)....

        返回:
        a map from processID to delay
        抛出:
